---
import LayoutCorporativo from '../layouts/LayoutCorporativo.astro';
---

<LayoutCorporativo title="Servicios" description="Soluciones Corporativas de Máximo Nivel — CISDE Ecuador">
  
  <!-- HERO HEADER -->
  <section class="pt-40 pb-20 px-8 lg:px-16 bg-brand-light relative">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-end">
        <div class="lg:col-span-8">
          <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold text-brand-primary block mb-6 gsap-reveal">Nuestros Servicios</span>
          <h1 class="font-heading text-fluid-h1 leading-[0.95] text-brand-dark gsap-reveal">
            Soluciones de<br/><span class="italic text-brand-primary">Alto Impacto</span>
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 pb-2">
          <p class="text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg gsap-reveal">
            Cada servicio está diseñado para potenciar la competitividad, la innovación y la transformación de su organización.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hr-gold mt-16 gsap-line-grow origin-left"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="bg-brand-light">
    
    <!-- 01: Proyectos de I+D+I -->
    <div class="border-b border-brand-dark/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0 min-h-[70vh]">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center py-24 lg:pr-20 gsap-reveal-left">
            <span class="font-heading text-[120px] lg:text-[160px] font-light text-brand-dark/[0.04] leading-none block -mb-8">01</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-fluid-h2 text-brand-dark mb-8">Proyectos de<br/><span class="text-brand-primary">I+D+I</span></h2>
            <p class="text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-[1.8] mb-10">
              Diseñamos y ejecutamos proyectos de Investigación, Desarrollo e Innovación que conectan la ciencia con la aplicación empresarial. Desde la conceptualización hasta la implementación, nuestro equipo genera soluciones disruptivas que posicionan a su organización a la vanguardia del mercado.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Investigación Aplicada</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Prototipado</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Innovación Abierta</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/contacto" class="magnetic-btn bg-brand-dark text-brand-light self-start">
              <span class="btn-label">Solicitar Propuesta</span>
              <span class="btn-arrow bg-brand-light"></span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-brand-dark relative overflow-hidden group gsap-reveal">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-radial from-brand-primary/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-48 h-48 text-brand-light/[0.04] group-hover:text-brand-primary/15 transition-colors duration-1000" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5">
                <path d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 01-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 014.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0112 15a9.065 9.065 0 00-6.23.693L5 14.5m14.8.8l1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0112 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.61L5 14.5" />
              </svg>
              <div class="absolute w-64 h-64 border border-brand-light/5 rounded-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-1000"></div>
              <div class="absolute w-48 h-48 border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-full group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform duration-1000 delay-100"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 02: Capacitación Avanzada -->
    <div class="border-b border-brand-dark/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0 min-h-[70vh]">
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-brand-accent relative overflow-hidden order-2 lg:order-1 group gsap-reveal">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-radial from-brand-primary/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center p-20">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 grid-rows-3 gap-3 w-full max-w-xs aspect-square">
                <div class="col-span-2 row-span-1 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-colors duration-700 flex items-center justify-center"><span class="text-brand-light/10 text-xs font-heading group-hover:text-brand-primary/30 transition-colors">LEARN</span></div>
                <div class="row-span-2 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-colors duration-700 delay-100"></div>
                <div class="border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-colors duration-700 delay-75"></div>
                <div class="bg-brand-primary/20 group-hover:bg-brand-primary/40 transition-colors duration-700 delay-150"></div>
                <div class="col-span-2 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-colors duration-700 delay-200"></div>
                <div class="bg-brand-primary/10 group-hover:bg-brand-primary/30 transition-colors duration-700 delay-250"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center py-24 lg:pl-20 order-1 lg:order-2 gsap-reveal-left">
            <span class="font-heading text-[120px] lg:text-[160px] font-light text-brand-dark/[0.04] leading-none block -mb-8">02</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-fluid-h2 text-brand-dark mb-8">Capacitación<br/><span class="text-brand-primary">Avanzada</span></h2>
            <p class="text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-[1.8] mb-10">
              Programas formativos de alto nivel diseñados para ejecutivos, equipos técnicos y líderes organizacionales. Metodologías experienciales, certificaciones internacionales y contenido alineado a las necesidades reales del mercado corporativo ecuatoriano.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Formación Ejecutiva</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Certificaciones</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Workshops</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/contacto" class="magnetic-btn bg-brand-dark text-brand-light self-start">
              <span class="btn-label">Solicitar Programa</span>
              <span class="btn-arrow bg-brand-light"></span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 03: Desarrollo Tecnológico -->
    <div class="border-b border-brand-dark/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0 min-h-[70vh]">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center py-24 lg:pr-20 gsap-reveal-left">
            <span class="font-heading text-[120px] lg:text-[160px] font-light text-brand-dark/[0.04] leading-none block -mb-8">03</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-fluid-h2 text-brand-dark mb-8">Desarrollo<br/><span class="text-brand-primary">Tecnológico</span></h2>
            <p class="text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-[1.8] mb-10">
              Construimos soluciones tecnológicas a medida: plataformas empresariales, sistemas de información, arquitecturas cloud y aplicaciones de alto rendimiento. Cada desarrollo sigue estándares internacionales de calidad, seguridad y escalabilidad.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Plataformas Web</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Cloud Architecture</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Ciberseguridad</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/contacto" class="magnetic-btn bg-brand-dark text-brand-light self-start">
              <span class="btn-label">Planificar Proyecto</span>
              <span class="btn-arrow bg-brand-light"></span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-brand-dark relative overflow-hidden group gsap-reveal">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-radial from-brand-primary/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-72 h-72 text-brand-light/[0.04] group-hover:text-brand-primary/10 transition-colors duration-1000" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5">
                <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="20" /><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="35" /><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="50" /><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="65" /><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" /><circle cx="100" cy="100" r="95" />
                <line x1="100" y1="5" x2="100" y2="195" stroke-dasharray="4 4" /><line x1="5" y1="100" x2="195" y2="100" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 04: Transformación Digital -->
    <div class="border-b border-brand-dark/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0 min-h-[70vh]">
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-brand-dark relative overflow-hidden order-2 lg:order-1 group gsap-reveal">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-radial from-brand-primary/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="w-40 h-40 border border-brand-light/5 rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-[135deg] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-1000"></div>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <div class="w-24 h-24 border border-brand-primary/10 rotate-45 group-hover:rotate-[225deg] group-hover:scale-150 transition-all duration-1000 delay-100"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-primary/20 rotate-45 group-hover:bg-brand-primary/40 transition-all duration-700"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center py-24 lg:pl-20 order-1 lg:order-2 gsap-reveal-left">
            <span class="font-heading text-[120px] lg:text-[160px] font-light text-brand-dark/[0.04] leading-none block -mb-8">04</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-fluid-h2 text-brand-dark mb-8">Transformación<br/><span class="text-brand-primary">Digital</span></h2>
            <p class="text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-[1.8] mb-10">
              Acompañamos a las organizaciones en su proceso de transformación digital integral: desde el diagnóstico de madurez digital hasta la implementación de ecosistemas tecnológicos completos que optimizan procesos, reducen costos y potencian la innovación.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Diagnóstico Digital</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Automatización</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Ecosistemas</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/contacto" class="magnetic-btn bg-brand-dark text-brand-light self-start">
              <span class="btn-label">Iniciar Transformación</span>
              <span class="btn-arrow bg-brand-light"></span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 05: Proveedores de Tecnología -->
    <div class="border-b border-brand-dark/5">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 lg:px-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-0 min-h-[70vh]">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center py-24 lg:pr-20 gsap-reveal-left">
            <span class="font-heading text-[120px] lg:text-[160px] font-light text-brand-dark/[0.04] leading-none block -mb-8">05</span>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-fluid-h2 text-brand-dark mb-8">Proveedores de<br/><span class="text-brand-primary">Tecnología</span></h2>
            <p class="text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-[1.8] mb-10">
              Actuamos como bridge entre su organización y las soluciones tecnológicas más avanzadas del mercado global. Evaluamos, seleccionamos e integramos hardware, software y servicios de proveedores líderes, garantizando la mejor relación costo-beneficio.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-10">
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Evaluación</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Integración</span>
              <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase px-4 py-2 border border-brand-dark/10 font-medium">Soporte Enterprise</span>
            </div>
            <a href="/contacto" class="magnetic-btn bg-brand-dark text-brand-light self-start">
              <span class="btn-label">Consultar Soluciones</span>
              <span class="btn-arrow bg-brand-light"></span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-brand-accent relative overflow-hidden group gsap-reveal">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-radial from-brand-primary/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-1000"></div>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-brand-primary/20 rounded-full group-hover:bg-brand-primary/50 transition-colors"></div></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 delay-75 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-brand-primary/30 rounded-full group-hover:bg-brand-primary/60 transition-colors"></div></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 delay-150 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-brand-primary/20 rounded-full group-hover:bg-brand-primary/50 transition-colors"></div></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 delay-100"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-primary/15 group-hover:bg-brand-primary/35 transition-all duration-700 delay-200"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 delay-150"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 delay-200 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-brand-primary/10 rounded-full group-hover:bg-brand-primary/40 transition-colors"></div></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 delay-250"></div>
                <div class="w-16 h-16 border border-brand-light/5 group-hover:border-brand-primary/20 transition-all duration-700 delay-300 flex items-center justify-center"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-brand-primary/20 rounded-full group-hover:bg-brand-primary/50 transition-colors"></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROCESS -->
  <section class="py-40 px-8 lg:px-16 bg-brand-light-mid">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-24">
        <span class="text-[10px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-bold text-brand-primary block mb-4 gsap-reveal">Metodología</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-fluid-h2 text-brand-dark gsap-reveal">Nuestro <span class="italic text-brand-primary">Proceso</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
        <div class="relative gsap-reveal">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 border border-brand-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary font-heading">I</span>
            <div class="h-px bg-brand-dark/10 flex-grow"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-4">Diagnóstico</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-relaxed">Análisis exhaustivo del estado actual, identificando brechas, oportunidades y vectores de innovación.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative gsap-reveal">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 border border-brand-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary font-heading">II</span>
            <div class="h-px bg-brand-dark/10 flex-grow"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-4">Estrategia</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-relaxed">Diseño de la hoja de ruta personalizada con hitos medibles y entregables concretos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative gsap-reveal">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 border border-brand-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary font-heading">III</span>
            <div class="h-px bg-brand-dark/10 flex-grow"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-4">Ejecución</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-relaxed">Implementación técnica con supervisión directa de nuestro equipo senior multidisciplinario.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative gsap-reveal">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <span class="w-10 h-10 border border-brand-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary font-heading">IV</span>
            <div class="h-px bg-brand-dark/10 flex-grow hidden lg:block"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-4">Evolución</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-dark/60 font-light leading-relaxed">Monitoreo continuo, iteración y escalamiento de las soluciones implementadas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</LayoutCorporativo>
